15 to a school board office or an at-large district to which more than one
16 (1) person may be elected on a:
17 (1) county council;
18 (2) city common council;
19 (3) town council; or
20 (4) township board;
21 must make a voting mark for each individual candidate for whom the
22 voter wishes to cast a vote. A voting mark on or in a circle containing
23 a political party device shall not be counted as a straight party ticket
24 voting mark as a vote for any candidate for an office described by this
25 subsection.
